{"contents":[{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26405900,"title":"Cover.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776453},{"data":{"format":{"p_vertical_align":"center","t_indent":true,"p_align":"left"},"is_anchor":true,"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":"导言","format":{"p_fontsize":3}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container","id":41108172},{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"中国地理","kind":"emphasize"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"中国幅员辽阔，山川秀美，陆地国土面积为960万平方公里，是排名仅次于俄罗斯和加拿大之后的世界第三大国家。她位于欧亚大陆东部，境内河流顺地势向东波涛奔腾汇入东海、黄海、和中国南海；陆地上则在其他三个方向上与其他国家接壤，从朝鲜直至越南。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"根据地势，中国可划分为东北平原、华北平原、南方丘陵地区、新疆-蒙古地区和西藏高原5个地理区域。地貌复杂多样，包括雪山、深谷、盆地、高原、平原、丘陵、沙丘、峭壁、火山口、低纬度冰川等。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"中国东部与南部濒临大海，拥有肥沃的低地与山丘，是农产品出产与人口最多的地区；西北部分布着低洼的盆地（即戈壁与沙漠地区），连绵的高原以及逶迤的山脉，包括地球上海拔最高高原的一部分青藏高原，这里农业生产条件差，故而人烟稀少。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"大体上，中国地势西高东低。山脉（占33%）、高原（占26%）和 丘陵（占10%）占国土总面积近70%。几个大型盆地部分区域被沙漠所覆盖，大部分可耕地与人口均位于低地平原（占12%）和盆地（占19%）。在中国，崎岖不平的地势为修筑内陆交通设施带来不少挑战。然而这种地势对于林业、采矿、水力资源和旅游业的发展却大有裨益，大量的梯田建设有力支持了农业生产需要。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container","id":41107615},{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"\"与我们一起探索中国\"","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"center"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container","id":41107617},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26553381,"title":"Map.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":41163405},{"data":{"format":{"p_vertical_align":"center","t_indent":true,"p_align":"left"},"is_anchor":true,"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":"西南地区","format":{"p_fontsize":3}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container","id":40777261},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26393880,"title":"001.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"羊卓雍措","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"羊卓雍措是世界上海拔最高的抽水蓄能站 - 羊湖电站的所在地。作为西藏三大圣湖之一，被誉为世界上最美的水。羊湖地处青藏高原一处满溢着千年虔诚与纯洁的角落，身躯曲折蜿蜒与绵亘不绝的雪山共同延伸至白云最深处。望不到尽关，湖水碧波如镜，倒影完整的天空与雪山，熠熠生辉。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776460},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26393470,"title":"002.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776461},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26394463,"title":"003.JPG","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"唐古拉山","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"唐古拉山位于中国西藏，藏语意为“高原上的山”，蒙语意为“雄鹰飞不过去的高山”，是青藏高原中部的一条近东西走向的山脉。唐古拉山雪线海拔5400-5500米，是长江、澜沧江、怒江等大河的发源地，终年白雪皑皑，高高矗立在雪山、草原和重重峡谷之上，被称为生命的禁区。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776462},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26394290,"title":"004.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776463},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26394518,"title":"005.JPG","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"布达拉宫","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"布达拉宫是西藏地区现存最大、最完整的宫堡式建筑群，位于海拔3700米的高原，楼层有117米之高，也是地球上海拔最高的大型古代宫殿。在这片离天最近的土地上拥有最酷烈的气候、最长的日照时间，最虔敬的宗教和最虔诚的朝拜者，是一处邸宅与碉堡相结合的藏族建筑，更是一座储存着大量珍奇文物的博物馆。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776464},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26394394,"title":"006.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776465},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26393268,"title":"007.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776466},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26394754,"title":"008.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"罗布林卡","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"罗布林卡在拉萨市区内位于布达拉宫西约2公里外拉萨市河畔，是西藏人造园林中规模最大、风景最佳、古迹最多的园林。园林布置既有西藏高原的特点，又吸取了内地园林传统手法，运用建筑、山石、水面、林木组景，创造出不同的意境。园林建造过程历时两百余年，以七世达赖兴建乌尧颇章为始，十四世达赖修建达旦米文颇章为止。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776467},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26394833,"title":"009.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"大昭寺","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"大昭寺位于拉萨老城区中心，始建于唐贞观二十一年，距今已有1350年历史，是西藏现存最辉煌的吐蕃时期建筑，也是西藏现存最古老的土木结构建筑。它融合了藏、唐、尼泊尔、印度的建筑风格，成为藏式宗教建筑的千古典范，金顶红墙雄伟而深厚，在藏传佛教中拥有至高无上的地位。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776468},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26394631,"title":"010.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"磁器口","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"磁器口位于重庆市沙坪坝区嘉陵江畔，因出产瓷器而得名，已有1800年历史，风景优美，人文荟萃，拥有“一江两溪三山四街”的独特地貌，有佛、道、儒三教并存的“九宫十八庙”和随处可见的茶馆。就着磁器口“三宝”听一段引人入胜的川剧，打发一个慵懒的午后，体会最重庆的休闲方式。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776469},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26394953,"title":"011.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"锦里","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"锦里位于四川省成都市，传说中西蜀历史上最古老最具商业气息的街道之一。茶馆、戏楼、美食小铺、手工作坊遍布街头，水岸、湖泊、荷塘、石桥映衬红锦灯笼。曾经晓看红湿处，花重锦官城的锦里如今已蜕变成一座微观的蓉城，在迷蒙的夜色和热烈鲜红的灯笼下盛情绽放。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776470},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26395129,"title":"012.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"蜀南竹海","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"蜀南竹海位于宜宾市境内长宁、江安两县交界之处，幅员面积120平方公里，生长着15属58种竹子。竹自古就有“咬定青山不放松，立根原在破岩中”的高洁品格，步入竹海，更是被其深邃静谧、活色生香的竹韵所感染，呼吸在深幽绝尘的竹叶清香中变得坦然，心灵在远离尘嚣、回归自然后得到沉淀。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776471},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26395021,"title":"013.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"九寨沟","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"九寨沟位于四川省阿坝藏族羌族自治州九寨沟县境内，是白水沟上游白河的支沟。因辖有9个藏族村寨而得名，海拔2千米以上，遍布原始森林，沟内分布108处湖泊。翠海、叠瀑、彩林、雪峰与藏寨，“五绝”风景因水而活，冷峻飘逸、轻盈灵动，安静优雅、斑斓神秘。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776472},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26395281,"title":"014.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776473},{"data":{"width":544,"layout":"C","seq":26395368,"title":"015.jpg","expandable":true,"height":362,"legend":{"data":{"paragraphs":[{"data":{"text":[{"content":"黄龙","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"},{"data":{"text":[{"content":"黄龙位于四川省阿坝藏族羌族自治州松潘县境内，背依终年积雪的岷山主峰雪宝顶，面临碧澄的涪江源流，高山雪水和涌出地表的岩溶水交融流淌，使流水潴留成层叠相连的大片彩池群，当光线照射时产生种种变化，形成池水同源而色泽不一的“五彩池”。","kind":"plaintext"}],"format":{"p_align":"left"}},"type":"paragraph"}]},"type":"container"},"dimension":"S"},"type":"illus","id":40776474}],"title":"华彩中国"}